Get Bundler 1.1.rc, then install gems locally:

$ gem install bundler -v "> 1.0.50" --pre
$ bundle install --local --standalone

Install imgkit's wkhtmltoimage at /usr/local/bin

$ bundle exec rvmsudo imgkit --install-wkhtmltoimage

Install a set of CA Certificates to verify Google Apps over SSL:

(Max OS X with MacPorts)
$ sudo port install curl-ca-bundle


Airplay Icon:
http://images.apple.com/ipad/features/airplay/images/airplay_icon.jpg
